    <section id="section-27186832" style="--block-base-text-color: 255, 255, 255;--block-base-link-color: 0, 26, 105;--block-base-background-color: 0, 26, 105;--block-base-highlight-color: var(--company-color);--block-background-color: #001a69;--block-title-color: #ffffff;--block-text-color: 255, 255, 255;--block-link-color: #001a69;" class="block--faq   block-padding bg-block-preset-custom bg-block-background text-block-text" data-section-route="section" data-section-model="27186832" data-section-sub-type="ContentBlock::Faq" data-section-name="faq">
    
    <div data-controller="blocks-faq" class="px-5 text-lg company-links">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[750px]">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl text-center font-company-header text-block-title" data-controller="fit-title">Working at Sage is built on three foundational principles:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li data-controller="blocks--faq--item" data-blocks--faq--item-open-value="false" class="border-b border-block-base-text border-opacity-15 last:border-b-0">
  <h3>
    <button class="relative flex items-center justify-between w-full py-4 pr-2 font-medium leading-snug focus-visible-company gap-x-4 text-unset" aria-expanded="false" data-action="click->blocks--faq--item#toggle" data-blocks--faq--item-target="button">
      Impact
      <span data-blocks--faq--item-target="toggleIcon" class="transition-all duration-500 transform">
        <i class="w-6 h-6 fas fa-plus"></i>
      </span>
    </button>
  </h3>
  <div class="overflow-hidden prose transition-all duration-500 ltr:pr-12 rtl:pl-12 text-md max-w-none max-h-0 company-links" data-blocks--faq--item-target="bodyContainer">
    <p>•&nbsp;Working at Sage means making a difference. You’ll create value for society by supporting education, research, and social justice initiatives, as well as contributing to the financial success of the business.</p><p>•&nbsp;You’ll deliver high-quality work and bring energy, curiosity and commitment to your role. We’ll recognize and celebrate your impact.</p><p>•&nbsp;You’ll be encouraged to make your voice heard and your contributions will help us to continuously improve how Sage operates internally. </p><p>•&nbsp;You’ll have the opportunity to support causes outside of work and broaden your social impact.</p>
  </div>
</li>

        <li data-controller="blocks--faq--item" data-blocks--faq--item-open-value="false" class="border-b border-block-base-text border-opacity-15 last:border-b-0">
  <h3>
    <button class="relative flex items-center justify-between w-full py-4 pr-2 font-medium leading-snug focus-visible-company gap-x-4 text-unset" aria-expanded="false" data-action="click->blocks--faq--item#toggle" data-blocks--faq--item-target="button">
      Independence
      <span data-blocks--faq--item-target="toggleIcon" class="transition-all duration-500 transform">
        <i class="w-6 h-6 fas fa-plus"></i>
      </span>
    </button>
  </h3>
  <div class="overflow-hidden prose transition-all duration-500 ltr:pr-12 rtl:pl-12 text-md max-w-none max-h-0 company-links" data-blocks--faq--item-target="bodyContainer">
    <p>•&nbsp;You’ll be encouraged to work in the way that best suits you to get things done.</p><p>•&nbsp;We’ll support you to create a good work/life balance that suits your lifestyle whilst also meeting the needs of the business.</p><p>•&nbsp;We’ll encourage you to think independently and bring your views to the table.</p><p>•&nbsp;You’ll have the ability to make decisions and progress projects autonomously.</p><p>•&nbsp;Depending on the location and needs of your role, you’ll likely have the flexibility to work from home or in the office, as well as plan your daily schedule in a way that best suits your life and working style.</p>
  </div>
</li>

        <li data-controller="blocks--faq--item" data-blocks--faq--item-open-value="false" class="border-b border-block-base-text border-opacity-15 last:border-b-0">
  <h3>
    <button class="relative flex items-center justify-between w-full py-4 pr-2 font-medium leading-snug focus-visible-company gap-x-4 text-unset" aria-expanded="false" data-action="click->blocks--faq--item#toggle" data-blocks--faq--item-target="button">
      Support
      <span data-blocks--faq--item-target="toggleIcon" class="transition-all duration-500 transform">
        <i class="w-6 h-6 fas fa-plus"></i>
      </span>
    </button>
  </h3>
  <div class="overflow-hidden prose transition-all duration-500 ltr:pr-12 rtl:pl-12 text-md max-w-none max-h-0 company-links" data-blocks--faq--item-target="bodyContainer">
    <p>&nbsp;</p><p>•&nbsp;At Sage, we’re inclusive, friendly, and care about each others’ mental and physical health. We support each other and expect everyone to embrace diversity and build strong working relationships.<br></p><p>•&nbsp;You’ll be provided with a range of benefits to support your well-being.<br>  </p><p>•&nbsp;We’ll support you to develop your knowledge and skills through tuition schemes and a depth of in-house training.</p><p>•&nbsp;We value continuous learning and improvement. We’ll provide regular feedback, as well as ask for it in return.<br></p><p>•&nbsp;Our technology team will enable you to work from different locations and effectively collaborate with colleagues remotely.</p>
  </div>
</li>

    </ul>
  </div>
